{"tid":1088206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估國家) 上車無位 大媽鬧職員「土匪」","createTime":"2019-04-02T01:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T02:23:11.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d025a564ad74307cec5da7099978557a93450a13","tid":1088206,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:26:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E9%AC%A7%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%9F%E5%8C%AA%E3%80%8D-222957244.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%258C%25AA%25E3%2580%258D-222957244.html&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m62LTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=29959fe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E9%AC%A7%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%9F%E5%8C%AA%E3%80%8D-222957244.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QckiWEAcJMnA.y_drjEGkg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9ODM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/2793fb8e08ff3d8a2af688c44e3abc7a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQckiWEAcJMnA.y_drjEGkg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9ODM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F2793fb8e08ff3d8a2af688c44e3abc7a&h=3ac79847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n職員引導內地女乘客返回車內。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】巴士座位有限，冇位就只好企，惟近日有內地客疑因上車後發現沒有空座而發難，更怒罵職員︰「你們像土匪！」<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁「巴士台 HK Bus Channel」發布片段，指在星期日（31日）早上有操流利普通話的女乘客，在深圳灣口岸上巴士，付車錢後驚覺已無空座位，要求落車及退款。<br />\n<br />\n據貼文所指，該女士在落車後向巴士公司值勤人員發難，指「服務人員」在她登車前未明言已無座位。<br />\n<br />\n根據片段，有疑似職員指着巴士的企位標示，大聲回應︰「你睇唔睇到呀，識唔識字呀？」其他人幫口︰「嗰度唔係有企位呀？」<br />\n<br />\n網民：坐少陣使死<br />\n該女乘客心有不甘，駁斥道︰「這麼兇，你們像服務人員嗎？你們像土匪！」有人回應︰「土匪雞翼呀？」最後她在一片吵鬧聲中，被另一名職員引導上車並返入車廂，期間豎起大拇指說：「真厲害！好厲害！」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民怒斥︰「坐少陣使死？」、「內地搭巴士都無這種規定啦！」有人則戲謔︰「畀司機位你坐好唔好」、「佢冇要巴士公司升佢上商務位／頭等？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個係土匪先<br />\n係咪以為係的士呀"},{"pid":"e38d4cd5bf3a292d95c06978893040fb49c8d1f2","tid":1088206,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我個腦自動彈左雞翼兩隻字出來"},{"pid":"d6c54b753e44b5c87bf04c083e902f0e0037b5e2","tid":1088206,"uid":45182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:28:21.000Z","msg":"死大陸哩 見到張圖 操流利普通話已經浮現腦海<br />\nDLLM"},{"pid":"fe664fb142488aaac1fcac5387f1c8c880de488c","tid":1088206,"uid":100406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:28:38.000Z","msg":"乘客心有不甘，駁斥道︰「這麼兇，你們像服務人員嗎？你們像土匪！」<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人回應︰「土匪雞翼呀？」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be15c5fdf9f9be5acc458829d2130d8df32a071","tid":1088206,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:28:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5786de425190f48e354de09564fd57333c62564d","tid":1088206,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1feef1bae473ff4e2ebb8d1b2109d381cef8165","tid":1088206,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:30:32.000Z","msg":"咁大間巴士公司<br />\n恰個手無寸鐵嘅女人仔...<br />\n真係似土匪"},{"pid":"2f63e5200b72c121ec0229b12fd769b1881e6663","tid":1088206,"uid":42815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e5b8a5c49702b8c367ed3925c14c2b0e6dc6e0","tid"